IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. WhitespaceTest.

DATA DIVISION.
01 ACCOUNTNUMBER PICTURE IS 9.
01 ACCOUNT-NUMBER PICTURE IS 9.
01 ACCOUNT PICTURE IS 9.
01 NUMBER PICTURE IS 9.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE 42 TO ACCOUNTNUMBER
MOVE 42 TO ACCOUNT NUMBER
IF ACCOUNT-NUMBER = 0 THEN STOP
IF ACCOUNT - NUMBER = 0 THEN STOP